{"id": "1406236357449224202", "channel_id": "1406236357449224202", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "昨晚我联络了MegaCrit，很幸运得到了在《忘却前夜》中自由参考《杀戮尖塔》中角色和IP的许可！这虽然不是一次官方交错联动，而是我们单方面的制作内容致敬，但对于我们来说已经超级激动人心！脑缸组的许多设计师都是《杀戮尖塔》的忠实粉丝，我做的底层游戏设计也深受其启发，他们的许可让我们深受鼓舞！因此我希望将这个消息分享给所有守密人！我们也向所有还没有体验过这款游戏的守密人推荐《杀戮尖塔》！\n\n预计我们会在游戏中加入致敬《杀戮尖塔》的无数值成长的长肉鸽模式，希望大家会喜欢！我们也欢迎任何大家的想法和建议！当然……这可能会需要很长一段时间！\n\nLast night I reached out to MegaCrit, and we were lucky enough to receive permission to freely reference Slay the Spire’s characters and IP in Morimens！While this isn’t an official cross-collaboration—it’s our one‑sided homage content—it’s still incredibly exciting for us! Many designers in the Brain-in-a-Vat team are devoted Slay the Spire fans, and my foundational game design has been deeply inspired by it. Their permission is hugely encouraging! I wanted to share this news with all Keepers. And for any Keepers who haven’t played it yet, we highly recommend Slay the Spire!\n\nWe’re planning to add a no-stats-growth “meat roguelike” mode as an homage to Slay the Spire in our game. We hope you’ll like it! We also welcome any ideas and suggestions—though… it may take quite a while!", "timestamp": "2025-08-16T11:21:14.224000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-16T11:32:55.328000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1356053116260454534", "count": 67}, {"emoji": "Emoji_AJE_M_04", "emoji_id": "1400771555939844149", "count": 23}, {"emoji": "Emoji_KP_P_02", "emoji_id": "1400771646293282918", "count": 5}, {"emoji": "Emoji_KP_P_01", "emoji_id": "1400771643743408210", "count": 5}, {"emoji": "Emoji_LT_R_02", "emoji_id": "1400771683664658433", "count": 9}, {"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 10}, {"emoji": "🥵", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "😄", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1406236357898276914", "filename": "IMG_1219.webp", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2134102, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1406236357449224202/1406236357898276914/IMG_1219.webp?ex=69cc56ea&is=69cb056a&hm=1f018445cfcaa728c0bc3405dfec015790af7320d61d8f24257a92632c0e9744&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1406236357449224202", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "前瞻：致敬《杀戮尖塔》Preview: An Homage to “Slay the Spire”", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1406236791459287232", "channel_id": "1406236357449224202", "type": 0, "author_id": "1388571537640001756", "author_name": "xingkongzhiyao_", "author_bot": false, "content": "肉鴿大概會做成甚麼類型的，需要自己組卡組嗎", "timestamp": "2025-08-16T11:22:57.700000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1406236357449224202", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "前瞻：致敬《杀戮尖塔》Preview: An Homage to “Slay the Spire”", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1406236866826731651", "channel_id": "1406236357449224202", "type": 0, "author_id": "1388571537640001756", "author_name": "xingkongzhiyao_", "author_bot": false, "content": "還有更重要的 會把打肉鴿的獎勵塞到排名嗎", "timestamp": "2025-08-16T11:23:15.669000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🤣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1406236357449224202", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "前瞻：致敬《杀戮尖塔》Preview: An Homage to “Slay the Spire”", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1406237014688399461", "channel_id": "1406236357449224202", "type": 0, "author_id": "557599119401811978", "author_name": "heikwok", "author_bot": false, "content": "先許願一下，想要個單角色闖塔模式(畢竟沿用4人1隊設計跟現在也沒什麼差別)\n每隻角色做幾種不同玩法的專造(例如墨菲沒傷害可以直接弄個新機制出傷如承傷或獻祭層數按xxx%倍率轉化出血中毒反擊觸傷/給敵人疊加或轉移身上的xxx%獻祭當作dot輸出等等)，然後加上各種舊/待測試造物\n給技能牌開局1級後面可以提升/能力成長也是可以讓玩家自選加血上限/雙暴/觸傷/基傷強效之類的屬性增益卡牌(當是加強版刻印合在技能卡上也行)\n\n個人期望是每隻角色都設計多個流派，然後效果放在專造上，精英戰後三選一，單場只能獲得一個專造\n假設後面如果有要開放突破100級也可以沿用這些專造機制設計讓玩家可以給角色往不同流派方向提升做一個新強化系統(甚至可以把模式當作是角色覺醒副本挑戰，不一定需要100級條件開放的門檻，只是舉例)，這樣做的同時，當玩家回歸正篇玩法4人1隊時也能得到反饋，由於角色可以往不同流派方向培養，隊伍組合跟玩法就多很多了(這點也是個人認為目前忘卻不足的地方，角色定位大多都鎖死了，變化太少了，特別是部分沒什麼輔助能力的主C)\n甚至不用一次做完，比如第一期先設計四小開放使用，第二期各界域出一兩隻角色這樣分批設計更新\n順帶可以當成舊角加強/新怪/新造物測試，參考後台數據再作調整也可以達到更合理的遊戲平衡", "timestamp": "2025-08-16T11:23:50.922000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-16T16:54:54.927000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "🙌", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "👏", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1406236357449224202", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "前瞻：致敬《杀戮尖塔》Preview: An Homage to “Slay the Spire”", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
